query:
/*+  */ select count(account.display_name)
from site AS s1
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.site_id = s1.site_id AND s1.site_name = 'math' AND t1.name = 'probability-theory'
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on tq1.tag_id = t1.id AND tq1.site_id = s1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on tq1.question_id = q1.id AND q1.site_id = s1.site_id
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.site_id = q1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id AND a1.creation_date >= q1.creation_date + '1 year'::interval
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.site_id = u1.site_id
inner join account AS account
on account.id = u1.account_id;
